42  * optvar=[ agent1_u, ..., agentN_u, \
43  * agent1_lambda, ..., agentN_lambda,\

46  * agentNc1_lambda, ..., agentNcM_lambda,

49  *
50  * ]
51  * x=[agent1_x,agent2_x,...,agentN_x]...
52  * =============================================== */

331  /***************************************************************************************
332  * Hamiltonian=l+lambda*f+mui*ci+mu*c
333  * =>dHdu=dldu+lambda*dfdu+mui*dcidu+mu*dcdu
334  * 0=dHdu for optimality
335  ***************************************************************************************/
336  inline void dHduPrimalBarrier(double *out,double t, double *x, double *u, double *d, double *p, double *xdes, double *udes, double* lambda, double* mu){
337  double tmp_u[dim_u_conc_];
338  memset(tmp_u, 0, dim_u_conc_*sizeof (double));
339  // for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){tmp_u[it_control]=0;}
340 
341  //Get derivative of stage cost dldu
342  dldu (out,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
343  //Get derivative of system function dfdx*lambda
344  dfdulambda (tmp_u,t,x,u,d,p,lambda);
345  for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){out[it_control]+=tmp_u[it_control];}
346  //Check if equalities exist
347  if(dim_eqcon_conc_){
348  //Get derivative of equality constraint dcidu
349  dcdumu (tmp_u,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,mu);
350  for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){out[it_control]+=tmp_u[it_control];}
351  c(out+dim_u_conc_,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
352  }
353  //Check if inequalities exist
354  if(dim_ineqcon_conc_){
355  //Create primal barrier derivative -tau*ci/dcidu
356  double tmp_ci[dim_ineqcon_conc_];
357  //Get constraint functions
358  ci(tmp_ci,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
359  for(int it_constraint=0; it_constraint<dim_ineqcon_conc_; it_constraint++){tmp_ci[it_constraint]=-primalbarrierfactor_/tmp_ci[it_constraint];}
360  //Get derivative of inequality constraint with calculated factors
361  dcidumui (tmp_u,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,tmp_ci);
362  for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){out[it_control]+=tmp_u[it_control];}
363  }
364  };
365  inline void minusdHdxPrimalBarrier(double *out,double t, double *x, double *u, double *d, double *p, double *xdes, double *udes, double* lambda, double* mu){
366  double tmp_x[dim_x_conc_];

373  if(dim_eqcon_conc_){

375  for(int it_state=0; it_state<dim_x_conc_; it_state++){out[it_state]+=tmp_x[it_state];}
376  }
377  //Check if inequalities exist
378  if(dim_ineqcon_conc_){
379  //Create primal barrier derivative -tau*ci/dcidu
380  double tmp_ci[dim_ineqcon_conc_];
381  //Get constraint functions
382  ci(tmp_ci,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
383  for(int it_constraint=0; it_constraint<dim_ineqcon_conc_; it_constraint++){tmp_ci[it_constraint]=-primalbarrierfactor_/tmp_ci[it_constraint];}
384  //Get derivative of inequality constraint with calculated factors
385  dcidxmui (tmp_x,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,tmp_ci);
386  for(int it_state=0; it_state<dim_x_conc_; it_state++){out[it_state]+=tmp_x[it_state];}
387  }
388  //Negate dHdx

390  };

396  inline void dHduAuxiliaryVariable(double *out,double t, double *x, double *u, double *d, double *p, double *xdes, double *udes, double* lambda, double* mu, double* mui, double* slack){
397  double tmp_u[dim_u_conc_];
398  memset(tmp_u, 0, dim_u_conc_*sizeof (double));
399  // for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){tmp_u[it_control]=0;}
400 
401  //Get derivative of stage cost dldu
402  dldu (out,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
403  //Get derivative of system function dfdx*lambda
404  dfdulambda (tmp_u,t,x,u,d,p,lambda);
405  for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){out[it_control]+=tmp_u[it_control];}
406  //Check if equalities exist
407  if(dim_eqcon_conc_){
408  //Get derivative of equality constraint dcidu
409  dcdumu (tmp_u,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,mu);

411  c(out+dim_u_conc_,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes);
412  }
413  //Check if inequalities exist
414  if(dim_ineqcon_conc_){
415  //Get derivative of inequality constraint with calculated factors
416  double tmp_ci[dim_ineqcon_conc_];
417  double* out_mui=out+dim_u_conc_+dim_eqcon_conc_;
418  double* out_slack=out_mui+dim_ineqcon_conc_;
419 
420  dciadumui (tmp_ci,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,mui,slack);
421  for(int it_control=0; it_control<dim_u_conc_; it_control++){out[it_control]+=tmp_u[it_control];}
422  //d mu*cia dmu=cia
423  cia (out_mui,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,slack);
424  //d mu*cia da=mui*dciada
425  dciadamui (tmp_ci,t,x,u,p,xdes,udes,mui,slack);
426  for(int it_slack=0; it_slack<dim_u_conc_; it_slack++){out_slack[it_slack]=tmp_ci[it_slack]-slack_penalty_conc_[it_slack]*slack[it_slack];}
427  }
428  };
